  "description": "Add Contact Page Redirect to Home Page Appointment Button\n\nConfigure the \"umów wizytę\" (book appointment) button on the home page to navigate users to the contact page with proper language routing.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the \"umów wizytę\" button component on the home page\n- Update the button's href/onClick to route to /<lang>/contact where <lang> is the current locale\n- Ensure language parameter is dynamically populated based on active language (e.g., /en/contact, /pl/contact)\n- Maintain existing button styling and accessibility attributes\n- Verify navigation works correctly for all supported languages\n- Test that the routing preserves any existing query parameters if needed\n- Ensure the contact page exists and renders properly for all language variants",
